Supertails - India's Best Online Pet Shop for Food and Accessories

At Supertails our unconditional love for pets everywhere keeps us focused on delivering the best and the most trustworthy pet supplies brands and products to our customers. We are a team of pet lovers who are dedicated to providing premium services to pet parents to make the experience of their companionship with their beloved pets more special. We make sure that through our comprehensive range of services - pet foods and treats, health and wellness products, accessories, toys, grooming products, expert vet consultation, training, supplements and many more - the bond between pet and parent remains strong and unbreakable. It is our privilege that through our online pet store we can serve the needs of the pet parent and the pet. Nothing pleases us more than the joy on the faces of the pet when they receive our goodies.

Why is Supertails the Favourite Online Pet Supply Store?

Supertails is the one-stop online pet shop for all your pet food and supply needs. We are engrossed in bringing to you the healthiest pet food products from the most sought-after brands: Royal Canin, Farmina N&D, Pedigree, Drools, IAMS and many more. Our extensive range of health and wellness products from the most trusted brands - Trixie, Kong, Barkbutler, Captain Zack, Petvit and Wahl among others - makes sure that your pet remains the healthiest and active. If you ever have any concerns regarding the well-being of your pet consult online with our animal experts to get personalised advice.    

The Benefits of Buying Pet Products From Supetails

Our SuperDeals, offers and discounts across our range of pet products make sure that the health of your pet is not compromised by the size of your wallet. What's better than exploring pet products from the largest assemblage of dog and cat items available online? Well, our one-day delivery without a doubt. It does not matter what type of pet you have - Dog, Cat, Puppy, or Kitten - our online pet store has all their needs covered. If you find that you need to return one of our items then our easy return policy and top-notch customer support will help you tackle this hassle-free. Supertails also gives you a platform to easily connect online with expert vets and trainers to discuss any pet-related issues.

Buy from Trusted Pet Supply Brands

Shop and explore at Supertails: the most trusted online pet store. Our large and ever-expanding product base is there to fully satisfy all your pet needs: dry foods, wet foods, pet treats, grooming items, supplements, toys, bowls, collars, beds, vet consultation, pet-carriers and litter boxes etc. If you want something for your precious pet, Supertails is where you are going to find it.
